{"tid":1525783,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"屌你老母又話睇星期六情況立《緊急法》？","createTime":"2019-09-01T02:57:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T03:19:47.000Z","uid":13754,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0b8501f0a4ce48d723b37f771ea779aed3186d88","tid":1525783,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:57:19.000Z","msg":"火又出咗，槍又開咗，成車地鐵都係「示威者」咁嚴重，要畀黑警打柒<br />\n<br />\n星期六過咗，仆你個街以為政府班冚家剷會磨拳擦掌，凌晨宣佈《緊急法》同我哋攬炒，而家班縮頭烏龜去撚咗邊度？<br />\n<br />\n到而家都唔出聲，完全冇再提《緊急法》，即係佢哋一心只係靠嚇<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老味，我以後唔撚再信乜撚解放軍、乜撚緊急法，唔使你哋撳掣攬炒，我哋香港人主動同你攬炒！<br />\n<br />\nIf we burn, you burn with us!!!!!!"},{"pid":"f9b71b96f2a59c123c0735c30d5c4594b7e42a27","tid":1525783,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:57:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721/831無獎問答遊戲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8DUzH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8DUzH7.jpg&h=4b81709e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lxqsagt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxqsagt.jpg&h=281798cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">試分辨以上事件</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YqzkvvH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYqzkvvH.jpg&h=849fcb35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月，機場見！</span></span>"},{"pid":"19ae802faab33cb619c06476ac82205dc9dfebff","tid":1525783,"uid":169079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:57:47.000Z","msg":"機場見"},{"pid":"597b5b6e674dd00aea270d82312ee97a127b1c5f","tid":1525783,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:58:20.000Z","msg":"